Product description

Compatible with Multiple Home Appliances

This RF wireless remote control lets you effortlessly operate floor lamps, table lamps and fans at home. Whether youre on the couch or in bed, control them anytime, anywhere, creating a cozy living space. During holidays, its super easy to turn Christmas tree lights on or off. It makes your holiday more relaxed and joyfulno wires, no hassle!

Space-saving Wireless Plug

It features a compact build that easily fits into any wall outlet, leaving the adjacent one free. The wireless remote function adds extra convenience. In the living room, you can use it to remotely switch on your floor lamp for movie nights and table lamp for reading. In the bedroom, turn on the bedside lamp without getting out of bed. In the kids room, remotely control the night - light to create a soothing sleep environment.This plug maximizes outlet space and simplifies your lighting controltruly a must - have for your home!

Flexible Magnetic switch

Choose your control style: mount like a traditional wall switch, attach to metal surfaces (like fridges or cabinets), or take it portableall options deliver instant, whole-home control without wiring hassles

Plug & Play

Pre-paired and battery included. Perfect for renters, temporary setups and tech-minimal lifestyles.

Specification

Color White
Control Distance Indoor range up to 100ft/30m, depending on local circumstances
Frequency 915MHz
Battery Type CR2032 Coin Battery (included)
Battery Lifetime up to 10 years
Magnetic Wall Plate Size 4.72 x 2.76 x 0.36 inch
Portable Remote Size 2.56 x 1.57 x 0.48 inch
Outlet Size(Dia x H) 3.27 x 1.5 x 1.26 inch
Input 100-120VAC, 50/60Hz
Output 100-120VAC, MAX 16A, 1760W(General Use, Resistive Load)
Working Temperature -13F~122F(-25C~50C)
Use For indoor use only.
Included in the Box Magnetic Wall Plate, Magnetic Remote, Single-socket 3-prong RF plug, CR2032 Battery (in remote), Double-Sided Tape, User Guide
